  "text": "Can you tell me the philosophy behind this mechanism of propagation of the bodily complex. I am raw. The second density is one in which the ground work is a being laid for the third density work. In this way it may be seen that the basic mechanisms of reproduction capitulate into a vast potential in a third density for a service to other self and to a self. This a being not only by the functions of energy transfer, but also the various services performed due to the close contact of those who are, shall we say, magnetically attracted one to the other. These entities, thus having the opportunities for many types of service which would be unavailable to the independent entity.",
